<p class="hamesh">١ Musil, Hegaz, P.١٨٥, ٢٥٨.<br>٢ Musil, Hegaz, P.١٨٥, ٢٥٨, The Geographical Journal, Vol., Cxvii, Part, ٤, ١٩٥١, Pp.٤٤٨, “The Ruins Of Quraiya”, By H. St. J. B. Phiby.</p> </div>